      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\n** New keyword Mechanism ->\n\nconst s1 = new Student(\"Ram\", 25);\n\nStep1 : create a blank object.\n\nconst obj = {}\n\nStep 2 : to add object from constructor\n\nthis = obj\n\nStep 3 : code execution\n\nthis.name = \"Ram\nthis.age = 25\n\nStep 4 : Return object\n\n-> Har ek function ke pass prototype property hote ha",
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\n** New keyword Mechanism ->\n\nconst s1 = new Student(\"Ram\", 25);\n\nStep1 : create a blank object.\n\nconst obj = {}\n\nStep 2 : to add object from constructor\n\nthis = obj\n\nStep 3 : code execution\n\nthis.name = \"Ram\nthis.age = 25\n\nStep 4 : Return object\n\n-> Har ek function ke pass prototype property hote ha",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
