      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "console.log(\"Hello World\");\n\nvar a = 107698;\nvar b = 10986;\n\nsetTimeout(()=>{\n    console.log(\"call me asap\");\n},0);\n\nfunction multiplyFn(x,y){\n    const result = a*b;\n    return result;\n}\n\nvar c = multiplyFn(a,b);\n\nconsole.log(\"multiplication result\", c);",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "console.log(\"Hello World\");\n\nvar a = 107698;\nvar b = 10986;\n\nsetTimeout(()=>{\n    console.log(\"call me asap\");\n},0);\n\nfunction multiplyFn(x,y){\n    const result = a*b;\n    return result;\n}\n\nvar c = multiplyFn(a,b);\n\nconsole.log(\"multiplication result\", c);",
