      "text": "- we solve this problem using promise chain\n\nlogin()\n.then(getUsers)\n.then(getOrders)\n.then(getPayment)\n.then(GetAddress)\n.catch((err)=>{\nconsole.log(err);\n});",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
