      "updated": 1781845923428,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "-> React.createElement method is used to create an html element in react js.\n    it takes three parameters\n    \n    i.) Type of element.\n\n    ii.) additional element like class, id, css related things.\n\n    iii.) content of that element.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "-> React.createElement method is used to create an html element in react js.\n    it takes three parameters\n    \n    i.) Type of element.\n\n    ii.) additional element like class, id, css related things.\n\n    iii.) content of that element.",
