      "text": "JSX - React.craeteElemnt se create karne ki jagah ab hm element ko create karne ke liye jsx kar sakte hai \n\nconst heading = <h1> hello </h1>\n\nReact.createElement(\"h1\",{},\"Hello World\");\n\n\nBabel ->it converts our jsx into normal javascript code.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "JSX - React.craeteElemnt se create karne ki jagah ab hm element ko create karne ke liye jsx kar sakte hai \n\nconst heading = <h1> hello </h1>\n\nReact.createElement(\"h1\",{},\"Hello World\");\n\n\nBabel ->it converts our jsx into normal javascript code.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
