      "updated": 1781937078663,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "React Props ->\n\npassing data dynamically from one component to another, then the concept of react props is applied.\n\n\ncard(props){\n    return (\n        <H1>{props.image}</H1>\n        <H1>{props.product}</H1>\n    )\n}",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "React Props ->\n\npassing data dynamically from one component to another, then the concept of react props is applied.\n\n\ncard(props){\n    return (\n        <H1>{props.image}</H1>\n        <H1>{props.product}</H1>\n    )\n}",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
