      "text": "=> ComponentDidMount() -> Component jab pehli bar screen upar aayega\n\n=> ComponentDidUpdate() -> to change screen over update\n\n=> ComponentWillUnmount() ->",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "=> ComponentDidMount() -> Component jab pehli bar screen upar aayega\n\n=> ComponentDidUpdate() -> to change screen over update\n\n=> ComponentWillUnmount() ->",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "2DRNpFT1_MSx2rNmTCg4p",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4075.635933588531,
      "y": 3957.429767136332,
      "width": 1809.8585205078125,
      "height": 375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bGi",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1836805021,
      "version": 644,
      "versionNonce": 1646795417,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782363000588,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "-> It's used to handle side effects like api calling timers etc.\n\n-> useEffect(()=>{\n        console.log(\"Hello\");\n    },[dependency])\n\n\nCases of Dependency ->\n    \n    1. Not pass any dependency : if we not pass any dependency in useEffect() then function Component will run number of times that number of times code inside useEffect will also run.\n                                        or, on each and every render.\n    \n    2. Empty Dependency array : code inside useEffect() will run only one time it not depend on Component function.\n    \n    3. Any Value : if any value passed inside useEffect() then it will run when the dependency array's value will change.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "-> It's used to handle side effects like api calling timers etc.\n\n-> useEffect(()=>{\n        console.log(\"Hello\");\n    },[dependency])\n\n\nCases of Dependency ->\n    \n    1. Not pass any dependency : if we not pass any dependency in useEffect() then function Component will run number of times that number of times code inside useEffect will also run.\n                                        or, on each and every render.\n    \n    2. Empty Dependency array : code inside useEffect() will run only one time it not depend on Component function.\n    \n    3. Any Value : if any value passed inside useEffect() then it will run when the dependency array's value will change.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CyQ336d4t7p4I6b-_OziH",
