      "text": "// context API\n// jab kayi sare components deeply nested hon aur ek component se dusre component me data pass \n// karna ho to vo hame  baki bache components me unnecessary expose karna padta hai. \n// Is problem ko solve karne ke liye react me context api ka use kiya jata hai. \n// it allows data  to be shared globally without passing prpops manually\n// ek  commmon stotrage area hai jah par sari value store hoti hai\n// aur ye value kisi bhi component me use ki ja sakti hai\n\n\n// Flow->\n// context -> provider ->  entire app-> any component -> usecontext\n// create context -> ye context area banata hai ya ye empty box crreate do gya\n// provider ->it is used for sending values \n//  use context() -> ye sabko variable ki value batega or ye provider ki value return karega.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "// context API\n// jab kayi sare components deeply nested hon aur ek component se dusre component me data pass \n// karna ho to vo hame  baki bache components me unnecessary expose karna padta hai. \n// Is problem ko solve karne ke liye react me context api ka use kiya jata hai. \n// it allows data  to be shared globally without passing prpops manually\n// ek  commmon stotrage area hai jah par sari value store hoti hai\n// aur ye value kisi bhi component me use ki ja sakti hai\n\n\n// Flow->\n// context -> provider ->  entire app-> any component -> usecontext\n// create context -> ye context area banata hai ya ye empty box crreate do gya\n// provider ->it is used for sending values \n//  use context() -> ye sabko variable ki value batega or ye provider ki value return karega.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
