      "text": "-> render kya hota h ????\n\n-> useMemo Hook\n\nuseMemo kisi expensive calculation ke result ko cache krta h taki unneccesary calculation dubara na chale.\n\nSyntax -> \n\nconst value = useMemo (()=>{\n    return calculation\n}, dependencies[])",
